Company Description                    




                        Nippon Electric Glass Korea Co., Ltd. is engaged in manufacturing and distribution of specialty glass products and glassmaking machineries. The company operates as a subsidiary of Nippon Electric Glass Co., Ltd. (Japan). Nippon Electric Glass Korea Co., Ltd. is based in Gumi, Gyeongsangbuk-do Province, South Korea.                    


