Business summary
Nippon Electric Glass Co., Ltd. engages in the manufacture and sale of specialty glass products and glassmaking machinery. Its products include glass for solar cells, flat panel display, Cathode Ray Tube (CRT), electronic, and optical devices. It also manufactures chemically strengthened and light-related glasses. The company was founded on October 31, 1944 and is headquartered in Otsu, Japan.







